---
title: Smashed Pork Gyoza Tacos with Pickled Veggies, Sriracha Mayo & Sesame Seeds
description: There's no need to choose between dumplings and tacos, thanks to this genius hybrid. We take flavorful pork dumpling filling, “smash” it over flour tortillas, then cook to sizzly perfection. Pickled cucumbers, shallot, and carrots add crispness and tangy flavor, and a drizzle of Sriracha mayo and sprinkle of sesame seeds bring it all together.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6682ebfe88a40e5df74250d6-0654990f.jpeg
